OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny overnight frost and fog
OL,6,Fwill soon clear to leave plenty of
OL,7,Fsunshine to start with on Sunday.
OL,8,FCloud will slowly bubble up during the
OL,9,Fmorning, limiting the sunshine this
OL,10,Fafternoon, though staying largely dry.
OL,11,FLighter winds than recently.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FThe odd shower is possible
OL,14,Fthis evening, but a dry night is
OL,15,Fexpected with clear spells and light
OL,16,Fwinds. A slight frost forming in rural
OL,17,Fareas by the morning.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
